          <l>I will always be</l>
          <l>Oh lonely</l>
          <l>So lonely</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>And now that you've found a friend</l>
          <l>You are loosing me</l>
          <l>I hear that you've found a friend</l>
          <l>And she looks like me</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>All your kisses were endless they made me forget what I wanted to</l>
          <l>I'll be looking for answers forever for some kind of clue</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="5" type="stanza">
          <l>Oh love me</l>
